  slug the-footwear-design-and-development-institute-act-2017
  handle (2255)
  collectionHandle 123456789/1362
  title `The Footwear Design and Development Institute Act, 2017`
  actNumber (20)
  enactmentDate 2017-08-04
  sourceUrl `https://www.indiacode.nic.in/handle/123456789/2255`
  sources obj_root_law_sources
  sections obj_root_law_sections
  hindiTitle `फुटवियर डिजाइन और विकास संस्थान अधिनियम, 2017`
  actYear (2017)
  ministry `Ministry of Commerce and Industry`
  department `Department of Commerce`
  longTitle `An Act to establish and declare the Footwear Design and Development Institute as an institution of national importance for the promotion and development of quality and excellence in education, research and training in all disciplines relating to footwear and leather products design and development and for matters connected therewith or incidental thereto.`
  enforcementDate 16-10-2017
  notification `S.O. 3248(E) Part-II s. 3(ii) 5-10-2017`
